Running out of ideas

23 Jan 2018

I really feel like I am running out of ideas for what to write here. My days are much the same, not a lot new happens, I think all the same thoughts, and I don't really want to write any more depressing entries. So I guess some random positive thoughts from today:

Overwatch League has continued to be really awesome, I am excited for this week's matches.
The start of NALCS was pretty cool, Doubelift is someone I have admired for years and to see him do so well is awesome.
I am really enjoying listening to the music of both McCafferty and Car Seat Headrest at the moment, and excited for their new albums this year. I really wish I was as good/bad at dancing as Will Toledo.
